translation[11]{c,v,t}:
  21,102,Wọn kò sì níí gbọ́ kíkùn rẹ̀. Olùṣegbére sì ni wọ́n nínú ìgbádùn tí ẹ̀mí wọn ń fẹ́
  21,103,"Ìpáyà t’ó tóbi jùlọ kò níí bà wọ́n nínú jẹ́. Àwọn mọlāika yóò máa pàdé wọn, (wọn yóò sọ pé): “Èyí ni ọjọ́ yín tí À ń ṣe ní àdéhùn fun yín.”"
  21,104,(Ọjọ́ náà ni) ọjọ́ tí A máa ká sánmọ̀ bí kíká ewé tírà. Gẹ́gẹ́ bí A ti ṣe bẹ̀rẹ̀ ìṣẹ̀dá ẹ̀dá ní ìbẹ̀rẹ̀ pẹ̀pẹ̀ (ibẹ̀ náà ni) A óò dá a padà sí. (Ó jẹ́) àdéhùn tí A ṣe. Dájúdájú Àwa máa ṣe bẹ́ẹ̀
  21,105,"Àti pé A ti kọ ọ́ sínú àwọn ìpín-ìpín Tírà (tí A sọ̀kalẹ̀) lẹ́yìn (èyí tí ó wà nínú) Tírà Ìpìlẹ̀ (ìyẹn, Laohul-Mahfūṭḥ) pé dájúdájú ilẹ̀ (Ọgbà Ìdẹ̀ra), àwọn ẹrúsìn Mi, àwọn ẹni rere, ni wọn yóò jogún rẹ̀"
  21,106,Dájúdájú ohun t’ó tó mú ni gúnlẹ̀ sínú Ọgbà Ìdẹ̀ra ti wà nínú (al-Ƙur’ān) yìí fún ìjọ olùjọ́sìn (fún Mi)
  21,107,A kò sì fi iṣẹ́ ìmísí rán ọ bí kò ṣe pé kí o lè jẹ́ ìkẹ́ fún gbogbo ẹ̀dá
  21,108,"Sọ pé: “Ohun tí Wọ́n ń fi ránṣẹ́ sí mi ní ìmísí ni pé, Ọlọ́hun yín, Ọlọ́hun Ọ̀kan ṣoṣo ni. Nítorí náà, ṣé ẹ̀yin máa di mùsùlùmí?”"
  21,109,"Tí wọ́n bá gbúnrí, sọ nígbà náà pé: \"Èmi ń fi to yín létí pé èmi àti ẹ̀yin dì jọ dá dúró fún ogun ẹ̀sìn (tí ó máa ṣẹlẹ̀ láààrin wa báyìí). Èmi kò sì mọ̀ bóyá ohun tí Wọ́n ń ṣe ní àdéhùn fun yín ti súnmọ́ tàbí ó sì jìnnà"
  21,110,Dájúdájú (Allāhu) mọ ohun tí ó hàn nínú ọ̀rọ̀. Ó sì mọ ohun tí ẹ̀ ń fi pamọ́
  21,111,Èmi kò sì mọ̀ bóyá (lílọ́ yín lára) máa jẹ́ àdánwò àti ìgbádùn fun yín títí di ìgbà díẹ̀
  21,112,"Ó sọ pé: “Olúwa mi, ṣèdájọ́ pẹ̀lú òdodo. Olúwa wa ni Àjọkẹ́-ayé, Olùrànlọ́wọ́ lórí ohun tí ẹ̀ ń fi ròyìn (Rẹ̀).”"